reviewText:
this game got a bad rap.
but it's wicked fun! I loved every bit of it. Replayable story, awesome perks, and cool weapons. I love the multiplayer also, but the one thing it sucks at is the Windows Live service. Just download the newest distributable here:
http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=5549
if you have windows 8, and this:
http://games.softpedia.com/get/Tools/Bulletstorm-INI-Editor.shtml
if you want to edit the game's encrypted INI files. (you definately will!)
